ROOT CAUSE ANALYSIS:
Railway default healthcheck timeout ~40s total.
Our health endpoint included database query (5-10s).
Startup + DB query > 40s = timeout = deployment fail.

SOLUTION:
- Extend healthcheck window to 75s
- Health endpoint responds in < 50ms
- Multiple retries possible within window
